data.description: Lock and leave or stay for a lifetime! This exceptional ranch style floorplan has just over 2100 Sq Ft of open super functional space with a covered private patio, that creates an extention of the living space into the cozy back yard.  Hard flooring throughout the living areas maximized the flexibility and helps make this the perfect home for entertaining.  The study/flex room could easily be a non-conforming 4th bedroom/guest room, or exercise room. The 3 car garage is oversized and the landscaping is finished. This home offers a wonderful lifestyle in the breathtaking setting of Spyglass Ridge, with numerous community parks, pool, and 7 miles of sidewalks and hiking trails, it's walking distance to the Community Center and down the street from Spyglass Ridges' own Dog Park. All of this is just eight minutes from downtown Grand Junction. Whether you like to swim, hike, bike, take your dog to the park or enjoy long walks, this property is a must to see.
